<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat her Hans
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als wir ew seins briefs ein
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slosze<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        brief. Nu ist uns sölich czwitracht sünderlich <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nicht liebe; und wer ew iht czesynne, daz wir
                                <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>arbeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das lieszet uns an
                            <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, was wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dar
                        czü getün künden, das sich czü <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> czüg,
                        das <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün. Wan wo wir ew etc.</ab>
</div>
